Nexus.Description:
Primary structure. Can receive gathered resources. Can use the Chrono Boost ability.

Enables:
- Probes
- Mothership Core
Nexus.Name: Nexus

Probe.Description: Basic worker unit. Can gather resources and warp in Protoss structures.**Can attack ground units**
Probe.Name: Probe

Assimilator.Description: Warped in over a Vespene Geyser to allow harvesting of vespene gas.
Assimilator.Name: Assimilator

Pylon.Description:
Provides supply.
Supply allows you to warp in more units.
Creates power for nearby structures.
Pylon.Name: Pylon

Gateway.Description:
Warps in Protoss ground units.

Enables:
- Zealots
Gateway.Name: Gateway

WarpGate.Description: Enables warp in of Protoss ground units.
WarpGate.Name: Warp Gate

Zealot.Description: Powerful melee warrior.**Can attack ground units**
Zealot.Name: Zealot

Stalker.Description: Ranged support strider.**Can attack ground and air units**
Stalker.Name: Stalker

HighTemplar.Description: Potent psionic master. Can use Feedback and be upgraded to use Psionic Storm. Can transform into an Archon.
HighTemplar.Name: High Templar

Archon.Description: Powerful psionic attacker.**Can attack ground and air units**
Archon.Name: Archon

DarkTemplar.Description: Deadly warrior-assassin. Cloak renders the unit invisible to enemies without detection. Can transform into an Archon.**Can attack ground units**
DarkTemplar.Name: Dark Templar

Sentry.Description:
Energy-manipulator unit. Can use Force Field, Guardian Shield, and Hallucination.

Can attack ground and air units.
Sentry.Name: Sentry

Immortal.Description: Assault strider. Can use Barrier to absorb damage.**Can attack ground units**
Immortal.Name: Immortal

VoidRay.Description:
Surgical strike craft.

Can attack ground and air units.
VoidRay.Name: Void Ray

WarpPrism.Description: Flying transport. Can load and unload units. Can also deploy to create a power field.
WarpPrism.Name: Warp Prism

WarpPrismPhasing.Description: Immobile power provider. Can load and unload units. Can switch to a mobile Transport Mode.
WarpPrismPhasing.Name: Warp Prism

Colossus.Description: Battle strider with a powerful area attack. Can step up and down cliffs. Can be targeted by anti-air weapons.**Can attack ground units**
Colossus.Name: Colossus

Oracle.Description: Flying caster. Can use Revelation, Stasis Ward, and Pulsar Beam.
Oracle.Name: Oracle

OracleStasisTrap.Description: Ground unit trap. Cloak renders the Stasis Ward invisible to enemies without detection.
OracleStasisTrap.Name: Stasis Ward

Adept.Description:
Ranged specialist. Can use Psionic Transfer.

Can attack ground units.
Adept.Name: Adept

Disruptor.Description: Robotic disruption unit. Can use Purification Nova to deal heavy area damage.
Disruptor.Name: Disruptor

Forge.Description:
Contains weapon and armor upgrades for Protoss ground units and shield upgrades for all Protoss units and structures.

Enables:
- Photon Cannons from Probes
Forge.Name: Forge

CyberneticsCore.Description:
Contains weapon and armor upgrades for Protoss air units and the Warp Gate upgrade.

Enables:
- Sentries at the Gateway
- Stalkers at the Gateway
- Adepts at the Gateway
- Mothership Core at the Nexus
CyberneticsCore.Name: Cybernetics Core

PhotonCannon.Description:
Primary defensive structure.**Can attack ground and air units**
Detector
PhotonCannon.Name: Photon Cannon

ShieldBattery.Description: Defensive structure. Recharges shields of nearby units.
ShieldBattery.Name: Shield Battery

Stargate.Description:
Warps in Protoss air units.

Enables:
- Phoenixes
- Void Rays
- Oracles
Stargate.Name: Stargate

Carrier.Description: Capital ship. Can build and launch Interceptors to make attacks.**Can attack ground and air units**
Carrier.Name: Carrier

Interceptor.Description:
Combat drones that automatically strafe their Carrier's target. Carriers may not attack without Interceptors.

Can attack ground and air units.
Interceptor.Name: Interceptor

Tempest.Description: Siege artillery craft. Attacks from long range. Can use Disintegration.**Can attack ground and air units**
Tempest.Name: Tempest

TemplarArchive.Description:
Contains an upgrade for High Templar.

Enables:
- High Templar at the Gateway
- Archon Merge from High Templar
TemplarArchive.Name: Templar Archives

RoboticsFacility.Description:
Warps in Protoss robotic units.

Enables:
- Observers
- Warp Prisms
- Immortals
RoboticsFacility.Name: Robotics Facility

Observer.Description:
Flying spy. Cloak renders the unit invisible to enemies without detection.

Detector
Observer.Name: Observer

ObserverSiegeMode.Description:
Flying spy. Cloak renders the unit invisible to enemies without detection.

Detector
ObserverSiegeMode.Name: Observer

FleetBeacon.Description:
Contains upgrades for Phoenixes and Carriers.

Enables:
- Tempests at the Stargate- Carriers at the Stargate
- Mothership from the Mothership Core
FleetBeacon.Name: Fleet Beacon

DarkShrine.Description:
Dark Templar tech structure.

Enables:
- Dark Templar at the Gateway
- Archon Merge from Dark Templar
DarkShrine.Name: Dark Shrine

TwilightCouncil.Description: Contains upgrades for Zealots, Stalkers, and Adepts.
TwilightCouncil.Name: Twilight Council

RoboticsBay.Description:
Contains upgrades for the Observer, Warp Prism, and Colossus.

Enables:
- Colossi at the Robotics Facility
- Disruptors at the Robotics Facility
RoboticsBay.Name: Robotics Bay

Mothership.Description: Ultimate Protoss vessel. Can use Photon Overcharge, Mass Recall, and Time Warp abilities. Cloaks nearby friendly units and structures.**Can attack ground and air units**
Mothership.Name: Mothership
